						<p>Thank you, glad you liked.</p>
<p>As I said to the doc, the question is whether the central idea is religious stuff, or the sheer randomness. I need to make it more of the one or the other, I think.</p>
<p>The time machine thing is part of the general non-sensicness (is that even a word) of the story. It jumps, it meanders. does it work? Not entirely sure! It was fun to write though.</p>
