						<p>You know, maybe the problem with the tequila/mercury/blood/Jesus thing is not that they&#8217;re too random, it&#8217;s that they&#8217;re not random <i>enough</i> &#8211; because there&#8217;s a Jesus/blood connection, one starts looking for other connections. I loved the randomness of the tequila/mercury, maybe the blood needs to be maple syrup or paint or artificial food colouring #12 or something?</p>
